1. Njihova dela *pokazuju* da su veoma hrabri. (Their actions *show* that they are very brave.)
2. Zvanični izveštaji *pokazuju* da je bilo više od 100 žrtava u zemljotresu. (Official reports *indicate* that there were more than 100 casualties in the earthquake.)
3. Ove slike *pokazuju* kako je grad izgledao pre 50 godina. (These pictures *demonstrate* what the city looked like 50 years ago.)
4. Učenici *pokazuju* sve veću zainteresovanost za programiranje. (Students are *displaying* increasing interest in programming.)
5. Aplikacija *pokazuje* trenutnu temperaturu u realnom vremenu. (The application *displays* the current temperature in real-time.)
6. Oni su *pokazali* da su spremni da preuzmu odgovornost za svoje postupke. (They *demonstrated* that they are ready to take responsibility for their actions.)
7. Novi podaci *pokazuju* da je ekonomija zemlje u oporavku. (New data *indicates* that the country's economy is recovering.)
8. Neki sportisti *pokazuju* neverovatne veštine na terenu. (Some athletes *showcase* incredible skills on the field.) 
9. Pored reči, gestovi takođe mogu *pokazati* šta osoba misli i oseća. (In addition to words, gestures can also *show* what a person thinks and feels.)
10. Ovaj grafički prikaz *pokazuje* kretanje cena akcija u poslednjih 6 meseci. (This graphic representation *illustrates* the movement of stock prices over the past 6 months.)